How to Use;
1. If you use this for the first time,
$ mkdir lib/
$ mkdir bin/
$ mkdir matrix/
$ make

2. If you want to estimate "Acceptance", etc.
$ make
$ ./bin/solid

3. If you want to estimate "Resolution", etc.
$ make
$ ./bin/getMatrix	(<-- generate Reconstruction Matrices)
$ ./bin/resolution  (<-- try Reconstruction)


* If you want to change filenames, please see parFile.dat
* If you have matrices you want to use, you can just do it as below.
* $ ./bin/resoluiton
